"""
dl_dashboard.py  —  DL PC
Live dashboard showing all 20 DLs.

Features:
  - All settings loaded from config.json (no hardcoded values)
  - Main PC IP section (top-right) with live ping status dot
  - Click any DL card to open a full detail popup
  - Threshold editor: change warn/block/stale fail counts from the UI
  - Summary bar: OK / WARNING / BLOCKED / STALE counts
  - Auto-refresh every N seconds (configured in config.json)
  - STALE detection: marks a DL grey if no data received in last N minutes
    (configurable via monitor.stale_after_minutes in config.json, default 60)

Place this file in the SAME folder as all other DL_PC files:
  dl_dashboard.py
  process_files.py
  register_logger.py
  network_sender.py
  stop_tracker.py
  config.json          ← NEW
"""

